# Installation
> `npm install --save @types/node`

# Summary
This package contains type definitions for Node.js ( http://nodejs.org/ ).

# Details
Files were exported from https://github.com/DefinitelyTyped/DefinitelyTyped/tree/master/types/node

Additional Details

 * Dependencies: none
